# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok china head coach ma liangxing said here on friday that his steel roses will rely on team work rather than individual skills in their women 's world cup opener against group d rivals ghana here on sunday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Ma"
                  :op2 "Liangxing")
            :ARG0-of (c / coach-01
                  :ARG1 (t / team))
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 t))
      :ARG1 (r / rely-01
            :ARG0 (r2 / rose
                  :mod (s2 / steel)
                  :poss p)
            :ARG1 (w / work-01
                  :ARG0 r2
                  :mod t)
            :ARG1-of (ii / instead-of-91
                  :ARG2 (s3 / skill
                        :mod (ii2 / individual))))
      :time (o / open-02
            :ARG1 r2
            :ARG3 t
            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "Ghana")
            :ARG0-of (r3 / rival-01
                  :ARG1 t))
      :mod (g / game
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 "World"
                  :op2 "Cup"))
      :mod (w2 / woman)
      :location (h2 / here)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s4 / sunday))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :location (h3 / here))

                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (a2 / and
                              :op1 c
                              :op2 (o2 / organization
                                    :name n
                                    :op1 "U.N.")))
                  :ARG2 (o3 / official)))
      :ARG1 (p3 / possible-01
            :ARG1 (o4 / or
                  :op1 (r / remain-01
                        :ARG1 (s2 / school
                              :quant (m / multiple
                                    :op1 1000)
                              :location (a3 / and
                                    :op1 (c2 / city
                                          :ARG1-of (d / devastate-01)
                                          :mod (t / this)
                                          :ARG0-of (h3 / have-org-role-91
                                                :ARG2 (c3 / capital)))

                                          :op1 c2)))
                        :ARG3 (c4 / close-01

                              :duration m
                              :op1 (t2 / temporal-quantity

(a / arrive-01
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "David"
                  :op2 "Miliband")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Britain"))
                  :ARG2 (s / secretary
                        :topic (f / foreign))))
      :ARG4 (c2 / country
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 "Russia"))
      :purpose (v / visit-01
            :ARG0 p
            :duration (t / temporal-quantity
                  :quant 2
                  :unit (d / day))
            :ARG1-of (a2 / aim-02
                  :ARG2 (t2 / thaw-01
                        :ARG1 (r / relation-03
                              :ARG0 c
                              :ARG2 c2
                              :mod (f2 / frosty))))))

                  :mod c2))

            :ord (o2 / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1)
            :part-of (y / year
                  :mod (t / this)))
      :time (d4 / date-entity
            :weekday (f2 / friday)))
